## Privacy Policy
This privacy policy applies to all of games that developed by Nexorium Games.

We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.
The game does not track users, does not use analytics, and does not send any information to us or to any external server. All game data — including settings and save data — remains entirely on your local device or Xbox console and is never transmitted off the device by us.

## Third parties
The game itself does not share any data with third parties, because it does not collect any.
Note that the platform you play on (the Microsoft Store / Xbox) may collect its own data, such as purchase records, achievements, or usage statistics, under its own privacy policy. That collection is governed by Microsoft, not by us. You can review Microsoft's privacy practices at https://privacy.microsoft.com/privacystatement.

## Children's privacy
Because we collect no personal data from anyone, we collect no data from children.

## Changes to this policy
If this policy changes, we will update this page and revise the "Last updated" date above.
